snippet.title: v6.9 Cutting Dreams at Dawn Trailer — Honkai Impact 3rd
snippet.description:
Honkai Impact 3rd v6.9 Cutting Dreams at Dawn coming soon! New S-rank battlesuit Sirin Miracle ☆ Magical Girl debuts!
Story Chapter XL, summer event After the Blood Moon Fades, and Honkai Impact 3rd × PROMARE crossover event to be released! Stay tuned!

Sirin: Sakura Tange
Vita: Yoko Hikasa
